{"tid":1309652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"辛灝年:六四的沉重教訓","createTime":"2019-07-12T09:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T09:59:26.000Z","uid":131782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd0330d7b428aa50edb82242ec58b3f319e524e","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被高喊了三十年的，和平理性非暴力，應該終止了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非分化，只係覺得佢講得幾有道理</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uxLc0tQp2qU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuxLc0tQp2qU&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=b2a25775\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uxLc0tQp2qU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">42:50</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原因一:<br />\n對抗香港同對抗中共一樣 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋只要有少少反抗，政府就開始將和理非嚟用嚟將我哋嘅反抗壓迫</span></span> 咁樣嘅話就只會令<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>政府，自由自在地繼續用政權暴力打壓我哋</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n原因二:<br />\n六四帶比我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血的教訓</span></span>就係，和平理性非暴力只會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻痺我哋抗爭嘅神經，削減我哋應有嘅反抗精神。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，並唔係叫大家唔好做和理非，只係想睇下會唔會有多啲人覺悟</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理為盾，勇武為矛</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不篤灰</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"039233bb1e74e2f1aff88ddd26d28a7ffb110c5d","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"dedc5c22cd19a7cfe1d7e6f8261c1e7ad0cfb3d4","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"74ac4148870c03f4cd578e08542deb540aa475d9","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:55:42.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ce354d918e54f5049574696f546330acb0b106ad","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"06b319889b2328abaed3d1f280d0ad1b8f19f4a2","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"f9077d462b1dfeaff2dbf614d2231b52d4292a37","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"779842f91466c5974684bc7cca90864c693801cf","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"562157f3190285d8381d2cb078e0a0d902c0f0e2","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"19932c5eeaf1e1c955380deb4a997b76b9a9f0de","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"6136a5cf1507889270e7ff42d819edf89f7b0eae","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"189f5a40015a7962ba8fea6560321ac2fe203787","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"11"},{"pid":"e5bf9a52dfb7bfcd0a9dc20b217522ccc8ff0c6b","tid":1309652,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"12"},{"pid":"fb53510ef4e136312